Dialogs.Dialog: ...You haven't sent me any e-mails these days.
Is that so？ I really haven't thought much about it.
But it's true. The number is decreasing.
You know... emm nothing, it's okay.
Haha, now I'm worried. What's the problem？
Well, recently... I've been feeling lonely with so few emails... I'm kidding.
I don't get many of your emails recently. Did you get bored already？
I see？ I'm not bored of it...
You know. Did you get tired of... kissing me？
Then , I think that it is usual to do. Probably.
Hey, why haven't you kissed me lately？
Eh... I wonder if I haven't. Isn't it different for each person？
I... I think I miss it.
(Hmm, she seems to be a little angry.)
I have something to tell you.
Emm... I wonder what it can be.
We haven't been on a date recently. Why？
...That's what I wanted to tell you.
You know, I'm curious about something.
You don't keep your date promises these days.
I want to cherish the promises we made to each other...
We haven't been on a date recently, right？
Ah. That's right, it can be...
I hate that kind of thing...
I kept silent the other day while we were on a date. You left me alone, didn't you？
There's something I'm curious about, can I ask about it？
On the last date you left me alone and kept silent all the time.
I wonder if I've done something to anger you. When you do that...
You left me alone during the last date.
Geez. If you apologize, don't do it in the first place.
I have something to ask... Is it okay？
It's okay, what do you need？
We... We haven't seen each other recently.
Well, I'm sure it's something like that...
I think if we are dating, we have to be together more.
A little of your time, is that okay？
Um... We haven't met so much recently.
Oh, now that you say it...
(She seems to feel a little lonely...)
You know. I think we are seeing less recently.
I want to see you more, okay？ Don't you want to？
Because you were speaking with some girls you seemed to be getting along with.
Ah... I see？ Just a normal talk, but...
...You looked like you were good friends.
Hey, are you friends with them now？ You seemed to get along.
Well, I think we're on good terms. Why do you care about it？
I see. Well, it's just a friend.
No, it's okay. It's not good to be jealous.
You seemed to be getting along with that person earlier.
I don't get along very well with other girls... I'm kidding.
(But I don't get along with other girls...)
How about it？ Feeling better, I hope.
My fever has dropped and I think it's okay if I rest a little more.
I was worried about that. I was wondering if your cold had passed to someone else.
I don't think so. So don't worry.
I'll be fine if I rest a little longer. Thank you.
You know... I wonder if this is my fault？
No way... I'm sure it's not. Don't worry about it, okay？
Is your cold worse？ Are you okay？
I'm okay. Papa said to take my medicine and go to sleep, and I'll be fine.
That's nice, but... I wonder if it's because of me you have a cold.
If it's your cold, it's fine to pass it... I'm kidding. It's okay, I'll get well.
You can send it to me.
If I were to do it, there would be no end to it, right？ But, thank you. I'm glad you say so...
Can you send it to me？
...Thank you. Those words are enough, don't worry.
Send that cold to me, please！
No... I don't want to see you suffer. Don't feel responsible！
I'm really sorry. I can only say that.
It's okay. If you're fine, then...
Don't look like that. I'm glad you came to visit me...
That's right. If I cut some apples, would you eat them？
Really？ Well, if you're going to do it... I'll eat them▼ ...I'm kidding.
Haha, it's okay. Then, I'll do it.
Thank you for today... When I look at you face, it cheers me up.
If that's the case, you'll feel fine. I'm waiting for your energetic appearance, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Yes. Papa said I was better, and got his approval to go out.
That's an exaggeration. My family has a doctor, so don't worry.
Your cold seems to be cured. I'm glad.
Thank you for worrying about me. It was thanks to my good rest.
You know... I'm sorry I couldn't visit you.
Ah... Don't worry. I don't think you could have come.
I'm perfectly fine. I'm training normally, so it's okay.
It was so bad that I couldn't go see you...
I see, I missed the chance to get a nurse... I'm kidding.
(You don't seem to mind, but... I could have go.)
It looks like you've recovered, so I'm relieved.
Thank you... Are you okay？ I kissed you, so...
I'm glad you are cured, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Thank you for your concern. How about you？ Didn't I... pass it to you？
I'm glad... I was wondering if I could get away with it...
Perfectly. And you, do you feel okay？
I see... I didn't get to kiss you...
How are you？ Everyone in the club was also worried.
They say that if you catch a cold, you'll get well if you pass it on to someone else. Is it true？
Take a good rest. You know, Papa says that the best medicine for colds is rest...
That's right. I have to put up with a lot of things now...
Hey, if you pass it to people, you'll get over your cold... Is it true？
How's it going？ I think you aren't getting enough rest.
That's right... I must not move that much...
It's said that a cold will pass when you send it to someone. Um... is that a credible theory？
Huh？ Well, I have to try it...
Do you want to try it？ That's... then... yes.
Huh...？ Isn't it really fine now？
It's on purpose, isn't it？... Yes.
Will you try again？ Then, because it's for you...
How about it？ Do you feel it's working？
Oh, I feel like I'm going to be cured. Thank you.
... So, did I catch a cold now？
Oh... I think, I'm feeling better.
I'm glad. It was a successful experiment... I'm kidding.
I really have to be quiet.. I wonder if it's okay.
It's okay. Thanks to you, I'm full of strength.
Really？ All that's left for me is to get rid of my cold.
But you know, I feel that my body has become lighter.
Really？ Then, if I catch a cold, come and visit me, please.
How are you？ Do you feel better？
Then it's okay. Take a good rest afterwards.
Thank you. I got my power back, I'll do my best to heal back.
With this... did you pass it to me？
I wonder about it. I'm feeling better.
I wonder if you can come see me if you passed it to me.
That's right... Sorry, I said something weird.
I can't count on that theory.
That's right, I made rice porridge. Do you want to try it？
Oh, thank you. Thanks for the meal.
Thank you for your visit today. I'll get well soon.
I'll wait for you. But, don't overdo it. I hope you heal soon.
How's your body？ How are you feeling？
I see. I'm sorry to worry you.
Are you all right from your cold？
I'm alright. It wasn't a big deal in the first place.
That so. But, don't overdo it today.
Oh. I have to be careful not to fall again.
How are you？ Now you can resume your training.
Yes, but I was the one who worried the most, okay？
I understand. Thank you, I'm okay.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ thanks to your visit, I'm completely recovered.
Amazing. Did it work to exercise normally？
Maybe... ▲高嶺＊＊▲ how about you？ Did you catch a cold？
I'm alright. I wonder if this is also a tennis club side effect.
Thank you for your visit. Thanks to it, I got well fast.
I'm glad... Now we can be together again.
And... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, how are you feeling？ We kissed and it transferred...
▲高嶺＊＊▲ thanks to your energy, I recovered.
I wonder if that kiss worked... I'm kidding.
Ah... Speaking of which, were you okay after that？ Didn't you get sick？
As you can see. I look like this but I'm pretty strong.
(What？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲ seems to be different from usual...)
Thinking of you. You know... can I ask you something？
Yes... emm, calm down a little.
Thinking about you... Sometimes words don't come out...
Then, in any way, I want to be with you...
I want to get a little closer...
Don't you believe it... I hope？
(▲高嶺＊＊▲？ She seems a little different from usual...)
After all... No... I'm sorry, forget it okay？
Ah, well... it was sudden. That's it！
I won't hold back. That's obvious.
So you don't have to hold back, okay？
I want you to love me a lot.
I want you to make lots of feelings that make you like me.
...What seems to be the problem ▲高嶺＊＊▲...？
(▲高嶺＊＊▲... I feel she's a little different.)
Hey, what is the matter ▲高嶺＊＊▲...？
Don't say it again... I'm already like this...
(Oh, isn't it a rare sight to see a bold ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Hehe, that was kind of cute. You know.
I'm not, rather I think that you're a lot cuter, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
(I knew it, the atmosphere is a little different, a little bolder...)
